{"tid":787390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友食食吓飯自己走咗","createTime":"2018-08-20T15:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T05:51:55.000Z","uid":101759,"like":7,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"816b1f424ef9cfbfcdc64548a1c2c0f0151b14b4","tid":787390,"uid":101759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"琴晚約咗幾位好朋友食飯<br />\n呢幾個朋友佢都識係共同朋友黎<br />\n但佢同呢幾個人無咁熟<br />\n我男朋友無啦啦話想一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時佢好毒無咩野講我都唔夠膽介紹佢俾家人同朋友識<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢今次話要一齊黎加上班朋友佢都識就同佢一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間我同班朋友傾得有講有笑佢偶爾講幾句但唔算講好多野<br />\n之後我地食完話食糖水 佢無啦啦話自己唔去走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢走得勁倉促我完全反應唔黎佢就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我班朋友都唔知咩事 有個仲問我你男朋友返工係咪太攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我返去問佢 佢話唔明點解我地講野氣氛咁hyper又話我地講野話題悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我未來唔會再夠膽介紹朋友同屋企人俾佢識<br />\n我好驚佢又自己走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪同佢唔會有咩將來"},{"pid":"57d634bc4b6d4edc76e3f6184ac0c11f4a2226f4","tid":787390,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"你朋友好小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76e86c2bd6eb9f68ede4d95282e5b9404807a70","tid":787390,"uid":101759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57d634bc4b6d4edc76e3f6184ac0c11f4a2226f4","tid":787390,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"你朋友好小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"朋友定男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e9cb0ac4e95cf08f48c092d968f719f2bd63c